{"tid":1296831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察=緬甸軍政府 ; 林鄭=資政昂山素姬","createTime":"2019-07-08T13:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:22:09.000Z","uid":26601,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b326e5d61ab6b5bc7625e28b92ef055cd2836989","tid":1296831,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:14:23.000Z","msg":"香港昂山素姬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fb5f023f5f1ddb3ce0fa81d22c6b6eaf17d212","tid":1296831,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:16:46.000Z","msg":"我地係羅興亞人"},{"pid":"7371acea2a9602e790d39778c880884a97b9ece6","tid":1296831,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f65f3c8744cd4ad00bf6593fd7980bd6f59fec","tid":1296831,"uid":51584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"羅興亞人大部分是在緬甸英治時期進入緬甸的孟加拉人，尤其是第二次世界大戰期間孟加拉V支隊的後裔，英軍當時為阻斷日軍通過阿拉干向印度推進，組建了一支由孟加拉人組成「孟加拉V支隊」。但英軍撤進印度之後，V支隊對日軍的抗擊微乎其微，反而大規模屠殺阿拉干地區的若開族平民。緬甸政府至今仍稱之為「孟加拉非法移民」。[16]根據英國人和緬甸人的記錄，V支隊燒毀了上百個村莊，屠殺了超過十萬名佛教徒，僅在一個邊境小城「貌奪」，V支隊就殺死了三萬多個手無寸鐵的平民，若開人稱之種族清洗。[17]"},{"pid":"9b6d4c4472c1761b75de1655b62cb10290227578","tid":1296831,"uid":221265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pu9N6Mel5J0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dpu9N6Mel5J0&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=2412f4aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pu9N6Mel5J0</a><br />\n<br />\n今集正正係講緊香港點變軍政府"}]}